# Layer Routing

| Layer | Path | Edit when |
|-------|------|-----------|
| Flow | `src/acquisition_helper/flow/` | Orchestration, state, HITL steps |
| Crews | `src/acquisition_helper/crews/` | Agent/task definitions |
| Control | `src/acquisition_helper/control/` | Registry, budget, planner, profiles |
| Tools | `src/acquisition_helper/tools/` | Serper, custom tools |
| Models | `src/acquisition_helper/models/` | Pydantic schemas |
| Reporting | `src/acquisition_helper/reporting/` | Markdown output |
| Config | `src/acquisition_helper/config/` | YAML only |

Do not mix orchestration logic into crew YAML or vice versa.
